AddToFunc IncVerticalSize
+  I ThisWindow (!Shaded, !Iconic) Resize keep w+10c   
AddToFunc IncHorizontalSize
+  I ThisWindow (!Shaded, !Iconic) Resize w+10c keep 
AddToFunc DecVerticalSize
+  I ThisWindow (!Shaded, !Iconic) Resize keep w-10c 
AddToFunc DecHorizontalSize
+  I ThisWindow (!Shaded, !Iconic) Resize w-10c keep 

